vironment within the strict bounds of the LA_OnlyHuman_Academic_Timeline paradigm.\n * \n * CURRENT STATUS: Skeleton Only. No implementation. No migrations.\n */\n```\n\n---\n\n### `SvartulfrVerse/engines/family_engine.js`\n```javascript\n/**\n * @file family_engine.js\n * @description Family Authority Layer. \n * \n * IMPORTANT: \n * - This is NOT a behavior engine.\n * - This is NOT a relationship calculator.\n * - It must remain a Knowledge Layer Only.\n * \n * Future Role:\n * - Single source of truth for kinship relationships.\n * - Single source of truth for dynasty relationships.\n * - Parent-child authority.\n * - Sibling authority.\n * - Marriage authority.\n * - Douglas-Bloodmoon lineage authority (Malachia, Noah, Jasper, Alyssa).\n * \n * CURRENT STATUS: Skeleton Only. No family data. No graph. No runtime logic.\n */\n```\n\n---\n\n### `SvartulfrVerse/engines/README.md`\n```markdown\n# Engines\n\n## Current Status\n**Skeleton Only**\n\nNothing is implemented. The files within this directory (`En_Core.js`, `relationship_engine.js`, `state_engine.js`, `family_engine.js`) are purely structural placeholders establishing intent, boundaries, and architectural responsibilities. \n\nNo legacy code has been copied, and no runtime behavior currently exists.\n```\n\n---\n\n### `SvartulfrVerse/Bootstrap_Report.md`\n```markdown\n# Bootstrap Report\n\n## Repository Structure Created\n- **Root Directory**: `SvartulfrVerse/` initialized.\n- **Core Documentation**: `/core` directory established for architectural governance.\n- **Engine Layer**: `/engines` directory established for isolated behavior/knowledge domains.\n\n## Files Created\n1. `README.md`\n2. `core/ADR-000_Runtime_Baseline.md`\n3. `core/Architecture.md`\n4. `core/Repository_Scope.md`\n5. `core/Rebuild_Principles.md`\n6. `engines/En_Core.js`\n7. `engines/relationship_engine.js`\n8. `engines/state_engine.js`\n9. `engines/family_engine.js`\n10. `engines/README.md`\n11. `Bootstrap_Report.md` (this file)\n\n## As